OL,3,CThe five Dumfries and Galloway Winter
OL,4,COlympic hopefuls who are going for Gold
OL,6,FThe opening ceremony at the Winter
OL,7,FOlympics takes place tonight (Friday
OL,8,F6th February) and five athletes from
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway will be hoping
OL,10,Fto bring home more medals for the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FHammy McMillan Jr from Stranraer is
OL,14,Fhoping to better the silver he picked
OL,15,Fup at the Beijing Winter Olympics in
OL,16,F2022. He is lead on Bruce Mouat's team
OL,17,Fand as well as this being his second
OL,18,FOlympics, he's also competed in six
OL,19,FWorld Championships - winning Gold at
OL,20,Fthat event last year.
