OL,4,COlympic hopefuls who are going for Gold
OL,6,FCurling is in his blood, his father
OL,7,FHammy McMillan Sr represented Team GB
OL,8,Fat three Games.
OL,10,F"I think the party line is that we
OL,11,Fwant to go there and win Gold, we got
OL,12,Fsilver in 2022, and it's the only
OL,13,Fmedal we don't have in our arsenal is
OL,14,Fthe elusive Gold medal which Team GB
OL,15,Fmen's haven't won since 1924"
OL,17,FAlso from Stranraer is Bobby Lammie,
OL,18,Fwho also picked up Silver at the 2022
OL,19,FBeijing Games.
