OL,4,COlympic hopefuls who are going for Gold
OL,6,FHe's also picked up medals in the
OL,7,FWorld Championships, including Gold
OL,8,Fwith skip Bruce Mouat.
OL,10,F"Everyone around the Stranraer area
OL,11,Fand Dumfries and Galloway as a whole
OL,12,Fhas been so supportive of myself - at
OL,13,Fthe last Olympics the full community
OL,14,Fgot behind us and it gives you that
OL,15,Flast spurt of energy when you're
OL,16,Fthere."
OL,18,FJust down the road, is their team-mate
OL,19,FGrant Hardie from Dumfries.
