OL,4,COlympic hopefuls who are going for Gold
OL,6,FHe also narrowly missed out on Gold
OL,7,Fagainst Sweden in 2022 and is Hammy
OL,8,FMcMillan's cousin. His parents curl
OL,9,Fwith an uncle being a former World
OL,10,FChampion and Grant has already scooped
OL,11,FGold at the World Championships. He
OL,12,Fsays he's looking forward to friends
OL,13,Fand family from across Dumfries and
OL,14,FGalloway heading out to support him
OL,16,FFay Henderson is also from Dumfries
OL,17,Fand just three years after the World
OL,18,FJunior Curling Championships, she is
OL,19,Fmaking her Olympic debut.
