OL,4,COlympic hopefuls who are going for Gold
OL,6,FFay has been curling since the age of
OL,7,F10, after being introduced through
OL,8,FPrimary School and wears the same pair
OL,9,Fof 'lucky' black socks throughout any
OL,10,Ftournament she is competing in.
OL,12,FShe told ITV Border "Friends,
OL,13,Fworkmates and family will be cheering
OL,14,Fme on in Dumfries!"
OL,16,FHer teammate Sophie Jackson also hails
OL,17,Ffrom Dumfries and her hometown has
OL,18,Fgiven her big successes. She won two
OL,19,Fof her three Scottish Women
OL,20,FChampionships there in 2022 and 2023.
